content.rendered:
Directed by Samit Kakkad.

Written by Sarthak Dasgupta. Sarthak Dasgupta. Sarthak Dasgupta. Seneca Mendonsa.

Cast Vivek Oberoi (JCP Jayant Gavaskar 1). Sonali Kulkarni(1). Luke Kenny (Michael 1). Santosh Juvekar (Avinash Mhatre 1). Akshay Poptani (Mowgli 1). Samiksha Bhatnagar (Irawati 1). Vamsi Krishna (Shiva 1). Sandhya Shetty (Paravathy 1). Shruti Srivastava (Sakeena). Arun Malik (Mr. Mehta). Krishnakant Singh Bundela (Chacha). Freddy Daruwala(unknow). Siddharth Menon(unknow). Chinmay Mandlekar(unknow). Nagesh Bhonsle(unknow). Hitesh Bhojraj(unknow). Rohit Pathak(unknow). Bhavvana Rao(unknow). Jaywant Wadkar(unknow)

Language Hindi.

Producers Durgesh Ashok Gupta. Sumeet Mishra. Percy Jamshedji. Gautam Talwar.

Production MX Player. Zee Studios.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 10

Status On Going (2022–)
